title: Taylor Swift - 1989 World Tour Live (audio) mp3
description:
I really enjoyed the 1989 World Tour Concert released by Apple but couldn't find a copy of the concert anywhere as an mp3.  So I converted it myself using Sony Sound Forge.    

Here's Taylor Swift's Sydney show of the 1989 World Tour in mp3 ripped at 320. 

Track Listing:

1. Welcome To New York
2. New Romantics
3. Blank Space
4. Trouble
5. I Wish You Would
6. How You Get The Girl
7. I Know Places
8. All You Had To Do Was Stay
9. You Are In Love
10. Clean
11. Love Story
12. Style
13. This Love
14. Bad Blood/We Are Never Ever Getting Back Together
15. Wildest Dreams
16. Out Of The Woods
17. Shake It Off
18. Blank Space (Instrumental)

Comments are appreciated
